ceably slowed down. My hair feels stronger and looks thicker at the roots. Highly recommend.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggejs8K3f46_text","label":"ggejs8K3f46_text","default":"<p>Alyssa M , Phoenix AZ</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggR8Dntg_js_text","label":"ggR8Dntg_js_text","default":"<p>My hair was dry, dull, and breaking constantly. This shampoo brought back softness and shine. It actually feels nourished instead of stripped. I’m obsessed.<br><br>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDZyeX6hpj_text","label":"ggDZyeX6hpj_text","default":"<p>Emily Johnson</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZq2xyEvxv_text","label":"ggZq2xyEvxv_text","default":"<p>“I noticed a visible reduction in hair fall after just a few washes. My hair feels stronger and healthier.”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaMc5gWG4c_text","label":"ggaMc5gWG4c_text","default":"<p>Michael Anderson</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggByRtk137z_text","label":"ggByRtk137z_text","default":"<p>I was dealing with thinning hair, and this shampoo has definitely helped improve volume and texture.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggb2U7k96dy_text","label":"ggb2U7k96dy_text","default":"<p>Olivia Brown</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4E9PtyVz__text","label":"gg4E9PtyVz__text","default":"<p>love that it uses natural ingredients. My hair looks shinier and more manageable now.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfBOGaF3BN_text","label":"ggfBOGaF3BN_text","default":"<p>Daniel Roberts</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYIMNCabmQ_text","label":"ggYIMNCabmQ_text","default":"<p>My hair feels much smoother and less prone to breakage since I started using this.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggISr3z6Yug_text","label":"ggISr3z6Yug_text","default":"<p>Rachel P , Columbus OH</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggiU79WjMaR_text","label":"ggiU79WjMaR_text","default":"<p>It’s rare to find a natural product that delivers results. The rosemary scent is clean and spa-like, and my hair feels stronger with every wash.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"}],
